{"tid":608144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"影藝有個賣飛妹好正～ 做過影藝 你問我答","createTime":"2018-03-28T02:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T04:51:47.000Z","uid":150588,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2a846a56e6b3f2e389a13581664ee48b6b8ced05","tid":608144,"uid":150588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:15:49.000Z","msg":"為左證明我曾經係影藝既員工 <br />\n當然要爆小小料比大家聽<br />\n影藝係位於牛頭角淘大  <br />\n戲院對面有間老麥 <br />\n上面有大快樂 <br />\n左面有貢榮 <br />\n右面有間老甜 <br />\n戲院前身為百老匯 <br />\n入面分別有三間戲院 <br />\n有1號2號3號院 <br />\n唔講你唔知 3號院仲係有lift搭（舊式戲院黎講已算係先進） <br />\n佢地既廁所係2號同3號院通用（所以經常有人睇完2院再匿入廁所等睇3院 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人想知再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能大家入黎都係想睇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位大佬 我搵唔返張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307bd75bced232c70d0381086f8fb9abe1e869d1","tid":608144,"uid":1991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T02:17:29.000Z","msg":"Hello無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf17a7f527a21affd5c0089783d5f6efea1003ae","tid":608144,"uid":106506,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"